Instruction: With the new good battery installed, use a multimeter to measure the voltage between the two output terminals/cables of the power supply module. Then, without changing any other connections, measure the voltage between the two input terminals/cables on Control Module 1 (the pair that is supposed to receive power from the supply). Report both measured voltages and whether any reading is close to 12 V.
