- load_cable_pos: Load Input Cable (+)
- load_cable_neg: Load Input Cable (−)

Instruction: With battery installed and all switches on, sequentially measure DC voltage between the two cables at the output of each control module (1 through 8) where it feeds the next module: first at CM1 output pair, then CM2 output pair, … up to CM8 output pair. At each point, measure between the local + and − conductors. Report where along the chain the voltage first drops from ~12 V to ~0 V; also note any module where the input has 12 V but its output does not.
